  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EFibromyalgia has been present for centuries; with documented cases reaching all the way back to the 1700s. It\u0026rsquo;s estimated that this debilitating condition affects over 6 million American aged 18 years or older, yet fibromyalgia remains somewhat of a medical mystery.\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp; \u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003ETreatments, for the most part, simply address the symptoms and the pharmacological agents used to treat the symptoms have side effects of their own.\u0026nbsp; This webinar will explore some exciting new research showing that Super Pulsed Lasers are offering hope for the Fibro patient.\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
